Description: Aria programming language compiler and toolchain
 The Aria programming language compiler (ariac) and supporting tools.
 .
 Includes:
  - ariac: the Aria compiler (LLVM 20 backend)
  - aria-ls: Language Server Protocol server
  - aria-safety: static safety audit tool
  - Standard library modules
  - Package ecosystem libraries
 .
 Aria is a modern systems programming language with a focus on safety,
 performance, and developer experience.
